subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. The new species is widely distributed in the Indo-Pacific Ocean ( Fig. 4 ), examined voucher specimens having been collected from the Maldives , southern Japan , including the Ryukyu Islands, and Fiji and oceanic islands in the Pacific Ocean ( Johnston Atoll , Marshall Island, Phoenix Islands , French Polynesia , Pitcairn Islands , and Easter Island). The species has also been recorded from Madagascar , northeastern Australia , and the Hawaiian Islands ( Smith 1956 ; Thinker 1978 ; Hoover 1993 ;
Randall et al. 1997a
; Randall 2007 ).
